where # is a number from 1 to 6 (for which slot your ability is in).<br>
<br>
for example, I made a hotkey for casting my Darkness snare.<br>
<br>
/doability 4<br>
/cast 1<br>
<br>
That automatically practices my sense heading (which happens to be the 4th ability in my abilities list) and then casts the spell in slot 1 (which is Darkness).<br>
<br>
The lazy way to train abilities...<br>
